properties.Name: BillOfSale
properties.Description: An agreement to sell a product or item to another party.

Columns.Name: ContractId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Contract.

Columns.Name: DateOfSale
Columns.Description: The date that the sale was finalized.

Columns.Name: PropertyDescription
Columns.Description: A description of the property being sold including serial numbers, manufacturer, model etc.

Columns.Name: EffectiveTransferDate
Columns.Description: The date that the transfer of property is to take place between the Seller and Buyer.

Columns.Name: BillOfSaleSection
Columns.Description: The text of the Bill of Sale, which traditionally begins with "Know All Men By These Presents...".
